channel.title: The People's Mix
channel.description: D:Fuse's signature funky progressive sound with a nod to the spiritual and his eyes firmly on the dance floor.
channel.itunes:author: D:Fuse
channel.itunes:subtitle: D:Fuse's signature funky progressive sound with a nod to the spiritual and his eyes firmly on the dance floor.
channel.itunes:keywords: David Guetta, Deadmau5, Gabriel and Dresden, Matthew Dekay, Sander Kleinenberg, Mike Hiratzka, Deep Dish, Max Graham,
channel.itunes:summary: Music is about life, music is about people. This is D:Fuse's hour to bring his favorite tracks from his live sets around the globe. Each mix brings you his signature funky progressive sound lush with percussive elements and a touch of melody. Never settling with just one sound, D:Fuse moves between House, Progressive, Techno, and Electro to truly deliver a sonic soundscape worthy of his status as one of America's premier DJs having played alongside Paul Oakenfold, Dave Dresden, Jes, Armin van Buuren, John Digweed, Sasha, and more. Find out more at www.facebook.com/dfuse.
